chatter 5 10
parallel leven 4
fit 250
n

tclout stat
scan $xspec_tclout "%f" pgstat
tclout dof
scan $xspec_tclout "%f" dof
set redpgstat [expr $pgstat / $dof]
log /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360221_1_before_error.txt
show data
show param
show fit
log none
if {$redpgstat < 3} {
set error_array [_pct_get_error_list {2 3 4 9} 2.706]
set error_log_file [open /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360221_1_errorlog.txt w]
set header_string "value,lower_err,upper_err,err_str" 
puts $error_log_file $header_string
foreach item $error_array {
set item [join $item ,]
puts $error_log_file $item
}
close $error_log_file
}
log /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360221_1_after_error.txt
show data
show param
show fit
log none
quit
y

puts $error_log_file $header_string
foreach item $error_array {
set item [join $item ,]

}
close $error_log_file
}

tclout stat
scan $xspec_tclout "%f" pgstat
tclout dof
scan $xspec_tclout "%f" dof
set redpgstat [expr $pgstat / $dof]
log /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360184_7_before_error.txt
show data
show param
show fit
log none
if {$redpgstat < 3} {
set error_array [_pct_get_error_list {2 3 4 9} 2.706]
set error_log_file [open /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360184_7_errorlog.txt w]
set header_string "value,lower_err,upper_err,err_str" 
puts $error_log_file $header_string
foreach item $error_array {
set item [join $item ,]
puts $error_log_file $item
}
close $error_log_file
}

}

tclout stat
scan $xspec_tclout "%f" pgstat
tclout dof
scan $xspec_tclout "%f" dof
set redpgstat [expr $pgstat / $dof]
log /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1050360111_5_before_error.txt
show data
show param
show fit
log none
if {$redpgstat < 3} {
set error_array [_pct_get_error_list {2 3 4 9} 2.706]
set error_log_file [open /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1050360111_5_errorlog.txt w]
set header_string "value,lower_err,upper_err,err_str" 
puts $error_log_file $header_string
foreach item $error_array {
set item [join $item ,]
puts $error_log_file $item
}
close $error_log_file
}

tclout dof
scan $xspec_tclout "%f" dof
set redpgstat [expr $pgstat / $dof]
log /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360215_0_before_error.txt
show data
show param
show fit
log none
if {$redpgstat < 3} {
set error_array [_pct_get_error_list {2 3 4 9} 2.706]
set error_log_file [open /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360215_0_errorlog.txt w]
set header_string "value,lower_err,upper_err,err_str" 
puts $error_log_file $header_string
foreach item $error_array {
set item [join $item ,]
puts $error_log_file $item
}
close $error_log_file
}
log /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360215_0_after_error.txt
show data
show param
show fit
log none
quit

show data
show param
show fit
log none
if {$redpgstat < 3} {
set error_array [_pct_get_error_list {2 3 4 9} 2.706]
set error_log_file [open /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360162_6_errorlog.txt w]
set header_string "value,lower_err,upper_err,err_str"

foreach item $error_array {
set item [join $item ,]
puts $error_log_file $item
}
close $error_log_file

tclout stat

tclout dof
scan $xspec_tclout "%f" dof
set redpgstat [expr $pgstat / $dof]
log /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1050360105_26_before_error.txt
show data
show param
show fit
log none
if {$redpgstat < 3} {
set error_array [_pct_get_error_list {2 3 4 9} 2.706]
set error_log_file [open /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1050360105_26_errorlog.txt w]
set header_string "value,lower_err,upper_err,err_str" 
puts $error_log_file $header_string
foreach item $error_array {
set item [join $item ,]
puts $error_log_file $item
}
close $error_log_file
}

show fit

if {$redpgstat < 3} {
set error_array [_pct_get_error_list {2 3 4 9} 2.706]

foreach item $error_array {

}

}

tclout stat
scan $xspec_tclout "%f" pgstat
tclout dof
scan $xspec_tclout "%f" dof
set redpgstat [expr $pgstat / $dof]
log /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1050360115_2_before_error.txt
show data
show param
show fit
log none
if {$redpgstat < 3} {
set error_array [_pct_get_error_list {2 3 4 9} 2.706]
set error_log_file [open /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1050360115_2_errorlog.txt w]
set header_string "value,lower_err,upper_err,err_str" 
puts $error_log_file $header_string
foreach item $error_array {
set item [join $item ,]
puts $error_log_file $item
}
close $error_log_file
}

parallel leven 4
fit 250
n

tclout stat
scan $xspec_tclout "%f" pgstat
tclout dof
scan $xspec_tclout "%f" dof
set redpgstat [expr $pgstat / $dof]
log /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360168_3_before_error.txt
show data
show param
show fit
log none
if {$redpgstat < 3} {
set error_array [_pct_get_error_list {2 3 4 9} 2.706]
set error_log_file [open /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360168_3_errorlog.txt w]
set header_string "value,lower_err,upper_err,err_str" 
puts $error_log_file $header_string
foreach item $error_array {
set item [join $item ,]
puts $error_log_file $item
}
close $error_log_file
}
log /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360168_3_after_error.txt
show data
show param
show fit

quit

parallel leven 4
fit 250
n

tclout stat
scan $xspec_tclout "%f" pgstat
tclout dof
scan $xspec_tclout "%f" dof
set redpgstat [expr $pgstat / $dof]
log /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360248_0_before_error.txt
show data
show param
show fit
log none
if {$redpgstat < 3} {
set error_array [_pct_get_error_list {2 3 4 9} 2.706]
set error_log_file [open /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360248_0_errorlog.txt w]
set header_string "value,lower_err,upper_err,err_str" 
puts $error_log_file $header_string
foreach item $error_array {
set item [join $item ,]
puts $error_log_file $item
}
close $error_log_file
}
log /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360248_0_after_error.txt
show data
show param
show fit

fit 250
n

tclout stat
scan $xspec_tclout "%f" pgstat
tclout dof
scan $xspec_tclout "%f" dof
set redpgstat [expr $pgstat / $dof]
log /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/2130360212_1_before_error.txt
show data
show param
show fit
log none
if {$redpgstat < 3} {
set error_array [_pct_get_error_list {2 3 4 9} 2.706]
set error_log_file [open /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/2130360212_1_errorlog.txt w]
set header_string "value,lower_err,upper_err,err_str" 
puts $error_log_file $header_string
foreach item $error_array {
set item [join $item ,]
puts $error_log_file $item
}
close $error_log_file
}

tclout dof

set redpgstat [expr $pgstat / $dof]
log /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360144_5_before_error.txt
show data
show param
show fit
log none
if {$redpgstat < 3} {
set error_array [_pct_get_error_list {2 3 4 9} 2.706]
set error_log_file [open /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360144_5_errorlog.txt w]
set header_string "value,lower_err,upper_err,err_str" 
puts $error_log_file $header_string
foreach item $error_array {
set item [join $item ,]
puts $error_log_file $item
}
close $error_log_file
}

if {$redpgstat < 3} {

foreach item $error_array {

}

set redpgstat [expr $pgstat / $dof]
log /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360230_1_before_error.txt
show data
show param
show fit
log none
if {$redpgstat < 3} {
set error_array [_pct_get_error_list {2 3 4 9} 2.706]
set error_log_file [open /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360230_1_errorlog.txt w]
set header_string "value,lower_err,upper_err,err_str" 
puts $error_log_file $header_string
foreach item $error_array {
set item [join $item ,]
puts $error_log_file $item
}
close $error_log_file
}

show param
show fit
log none
if {$redpgstat < 3} {

foreach item $error_array {

}

set redpgstat [expr $pgstat / $dof]
log /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360233_0_before_error.txt
show data
show param
show fit
log none
if {$redpgstat < 3} {
set error_array [_pct_get_error_list {2 3 4 9} 2.706]
set error_log_file [open /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360233_0_errorlog.txt w]
set header_string "value,lower_err,upper_err,err_str" 
puts $error_log_file $header_string
foreach item $error_array {
set item [join $item ,]
puts $error_log_file $item
}
close $error_log_file
}

show param
show fit
log none
if {$redpgstat < 3} {
set error_array [_pct_get_error_list {2 3 4 9} 2.706]
set error_log_file [open /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360130_3_errorlog.txt w]
set header_string "value,lower_err,upper_err,err_str"

foreach item $error_array {
set item [join $item ,]
puts $error_log_file $item
}

none
none
backgrnd /home/thaddaeus/FMU/Steiner/thaddaeus/1050360113/jspipe/js_ni1050360113_0mpu7_silver_GTI0.bg
response /home/thaddaeus/FMU/Steiner/thaddaeus/nicer_d49_55575341.rmf
arf /home/thaddaeus/FMU/Steiner/thaddaeus/nicer_d49_55575341.arf
ignore **-0.5 1.5-2.3 10.0-**
ignore bad
source /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/common.tcl
statistic pgstat
setp back on
model tbabs(diskbb+nthcomp)
3.2107 , 2 2 5 5
, , 0.2 0.2 2 3
, , 0.1 0.1 1000000000 1000000000
, , 1.1 1.2 3.5 4
50
=p2
1
0

freeze 1 5
chatter 5 10
parallel leven 4
fit 250
n

tclout stat
scan $xspec_tclout "%f" pgstat
tclout dof
scan $xspec_tclout "%f" dof
set redpgstat [expr $pgstat / $dof]
log /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1050360113_0_before_error.txt
show data
show param
show fit
log none
if {$redpgstat < 3} {
set error_array [_pct_get_error_list {2 3 4 9} 2.706]
set error_log_file [open /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1050360113_0_errorlog.txt w]
set header_string "value,lower_err,upper_err,err_str" 
puts $error_log_file $header_string
foreach item $error_array {
set item [join $item ,]
puts $error_log_file $item
}
close $error_log_file
}
log /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1050360113_0_after_error.txt
show data
show param
show fit
log none
quit
y
sleep 0.5

set error_log_file [open /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360203_1_errorlog.txt w]
set header_string "value,lower_err,upper_err,err_str" 
puts $error_log_file $header_string
foreach item $error_array {
set item [join $item ,]
puts $error_log_file $item
}
close $error_log_file
}
log /home/thaddaeus/GitHub/MAXI-J1535/code/xspec_related/spectral_routines/dec-28-21/logs/1130360203_1_after_error.txt
show data
show param
show fit
log none
quit
y
sleep 0.5
